<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://bookshop.org/p/books/people-collide-isle-mcelroy/19879431/?aid=132" class="external" target="_blank">People Collide</a> <em>by Isle McElroy</em> <em>is available now from HarperVia.</em></p>
</span>
									
																		
